            <title>Apple 十大庫存見底產品，外媒：產品即將被淘汰現在不宜買</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/03/apple-63/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-63</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/03/apple-63/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 11:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[平板電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音樂耳機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 15]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 15 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 15 Pro Max]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1260385</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">根據</span><span lang="ZH-TW">外媒報道</span><span lang="ZH-TW">，</span>Apple <span lang="ZH-TW">即將於 </span>9 <span lang="ZH-TW">月 </span>10 <span lang="ZH-TW">日舉辦年度秋季發表會，預計會推出新一代 </span>iPhone 16 <span lang="ZH-TW">系列以及多款新產品。隨著發表會日期臨近，</span>Apple <span lang="ZH-TW">各大實體門市的庫存量顯著減少，外界普遍認為是新產品即將登場、舊款產品將被淘汰的徵兆。</span></p></div><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1260394 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240903at-15-694x322.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="322" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240903at-15-694x322.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240903at-15.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲多款 Apple 產品或將被淘汰（圖片來源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/08/25/apple-discontinued-products/">9to5Mac</a>）</p><div></div><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">多</span><span lang="ZH-TW">間</span><span lang="ZH-TW">外媒指出，</span>Apple <span lang="ZH-TW">過去廣受批評的 </span>FineWoven <span lang="ZH-TW">材質產品，包括 </span>iPhone <span lang="ZH-TW">保護殼和 </span>Apple Watch <span lang="ZH-TW">錶帶，目前庫存量已降至歷史新低，</span><span lang="ZH-TW">代表  </span>Apple <span lang="ZH-TW">有可能</span><span lang="ZH-TW">將全面淘汰材質，並推出全新材質的替代產品。</span>Apple <span lang="ZH-TW">多款 </span>iPhone <span lang="ZH-TW">機型</span><span lang="ZH-TW">亦</span><span lang="ZH-TW">面臨同樣的庫存緊張狀況。</span><span lang="ZH-TW">尤其</span><span lang="ZH-TW">是即將發布的 </span>iPhone 16 <span lang="ZH-TW">系列，甚至連主打平價市場的 </span>iPhone SE 3 <span lang="ZH-TW">的現貨數量</span><span lang="ZH-TW">亦</span><span lang="ZH-TW">開始減少，</span><span lang="ZH-TW">引來外媒推測或有新一代平價機面世。</span></p></div><div></div><div><p>9to5mac <span lang="ZH-TW">建議消費者暫緩購買包括 </span>iPhone 15 Pro<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>iPhone 15 Pro Max<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>iPhone 14 Plus<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>iPhone 13<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>Apple Watch Series 9<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>Apple Watch Ultra 2<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>Apple Watch SE 2<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>AirPods 2<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>AirPods 3<span lang="ZH-TW">、</span>iPad mini 6 <span lang="ZH-TW">以及 </span>iPad 10 <span lang="ZH-TW">在內的 </span>10 <span lang="ZH-TW">款產品。</span>9to5mac <span lang="ZH-TW">認為，除非有迫切需求，否則應等待發表會後再決定是否購買。</span><span lang="ZH-TW">消費者可能</span><span lang="ZH-TW">有機會購買到新一代產品，</span><span lang="ZH-TW">或</span><span lang="ZH-TW">可以優惠價格購入舊款產品。</span></p></div><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2024/08/25/apple-discontinued-products/">9to5Mac</a>、<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2024/08/29/apple-likely-to-discontinue-these-10-products/">MacRumors</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/28/apple-watch-coolz-app-face/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】Apple Watch 過百款錶面免費玩　可設定動畫錶面</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/apple-intelligence-7-functions/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學+實試】Apple Intelligence 7 大實用功能　一鍵校對英文文法 + TLDR 長文總結 + 錄音即時轉文字</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】香港都可用 Apple Intelligence　安裝方法 + 申請教學</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/03/apple-63/mobile-phone/">Apple 十大庫存見底產品，外媒：產品即將被淘汰現在不宜買</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/03/apple-63/mobile-phone/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
