        <item>
            <title>Elon Musk 用 Starlink 違抗巴西法院禁令，網民透過衞星仍上到 X 平台</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/03/starlink-x/software/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=starlink-x</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/03/starlink-x/software/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 08:00:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[應用軟件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交網絡]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Anatel]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Starlink]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[x]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1260278</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">馬斯克</span><span lang="ZH-TW">旗下</span><span lang="ZH-TW">衞星互聯網供應商 </span>Starlink <span lang="ZH-TW">向巴西電信監管機構 </span>Anatel <span lang="ZH-TW">表示，在其當地賬户解凍前，不會遵守法院下令關閉 </span>X <span lang="ZH-TW">社交平台的命令。</span>Anatel <span lang="ZH-TW">證實消息，並透露負責人 </span>Carlos Baigorri <span lang="ZH-TW">已經將此通知轉交至巴西最高法院。</span></p></div><div><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1260279 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240903at-3-694x460.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240903at-3-694x460.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240903at-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲Starlink <span lang="ZH-TW">向巴西電信監管機構 </span>Anatel <span lang="ZH-TW">表示，在其當地賬户解凍前，不會遵守法院下令關閉 </span>X <span lang="ZH-TW">的命令（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/starlink-tells-brazil-regulator-it-will-not-comply-with-x-suspension-2024-09-02/">Reuters</a>）</span></p><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW">上週，巴西最高法院法官 </span>Alexandre de Moraes 以「X <span lang="ZH-TW">在巴西沒有合法代表</span>」為由，<span lang="ZH-TW">下令國內所有電信供應商關閉 </span>X <span lang="ZH-TW">社交平台</span><span lang="ZH-TW">。決</span><span lang="ZH-TW">議</span><span lang="ZH-TW">同時導致 </span>Starlink <span lang="ZH-TW">在巴西的銀行賬户被凍結。馬斯克回應事件，指 </span>Moraes <span lang="ZH-TW">是「獨裁者」。</span></p></div><p>早前，巴西政府要求 X 提供<span lang="ZH-TW">部分文件不果，裁定 X 需支付罰款，惟 Starlink 未有如期為 X 繳交罰款而被凍結賬户。巴西</span><span lang="ZH-TW">最高法院</span><span lang="ZH-TW">暫</span><span lang="ZH-TW">未對事</span><span lang="ZH-TW">件</span><span lang="ZH-TW">作出回應。</span></p><div></div><p>資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/starlink-tells-brazil-regulator-it-will-not-comply-with-x-suspension-2024-09-02/">Reuters</a>、<a href="https://www.cnbc.com/2024/09/02/starlink-tells-brazil-regulator-it-will-not-comply-with-x-suspension.html">CNBC</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/23/asus-ally-x/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】Asus ROG Ally X 暢玩《黑神話：悟空》  優化及最佳設定 Tips</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/22/moshowtoysblitzwaygetter/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】模壽 x BLITZWAY 真三一萬能俠　LED 燈效驚艷 + 跳齒式關節</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/27/fujifilm-x-t50-review/dc/dc-test/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】FUJIFILM X-T50 輕巧高像素相機  5 軸防手震效果強 + 4020 萬像素細緻影像實拍</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/03/starlink-x/software/">Elon Musk 用 Starlink 違抗巴西法院禁令，網民透過衞星仍上到 X 平台</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
