            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Microsoft 近日於官方 Instagram 轉發一條影片，片中的藝術家 afsigned 以遮罩及切割方式重製出 Microsoft 經典繪圖軟件小畫家的介面，勾起不少人的童年回憶，觀看次數於短時間內已超過 176 萬次，引起網民熱議。</p><p>afsigned<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>首先製作小畫家的底部調色板及左側工具清單，他將調色板的對應顏色塗滿，並用膠紙將其他部分遮蓋，用噴漆完成工具清單，再一步步重現整個小畫家介面。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-47.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-47-359x580.jpg" alt="" width="359" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-47-359x580.jpg 359w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-47.jpg 557w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 359px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-48.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260211" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-48-359x580.jpg" alt="" width="359" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-48-359x580.jpg 359w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-48.jpg 557w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 359px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-49.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260212" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-49-359x580.jpg" alt="" width="359" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-49-359x580.jpg 359w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-49.jpg 557w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 359px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-50.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260213" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-50-359x580.jpg" alt="" width="359" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-50-359x580.jpg 359w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-50.jpg 557w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 359px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-51.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260214" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-51-359x580.jpg" alt="" width="359" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-51-359x580.jpg 359w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-51.jpg 557w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 359px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-52.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260215" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-52-359x580.jpg" alt="" width="359" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-52-359x580.jpg 359w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-52.jpg 557w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 359px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-53.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1260217" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-53-390x580.jpg" alt="" width="390" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot20240902at-53-390x580.jpg 390w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-c